.rule_6_6_2_ensure_login_class_is_set_for_all_users_accounts

Reference: Juniper Networks (http://www.juniper.net/techpubs/en_US/junos9.5/information-
products/topic-collections/swconfig-system-basics/frameset.html)
Requirement 7.1.

Remediation: Configure a class for a user account using the following command under the [edit system
login] hierarchy:
[edit system login]
user@host#set user <username> class <class name>

.